# Test code must stay in the public repo but never ship in the runtime image.
# The build runs only `go build`, which ignores these; CI tests from a repo
# checkout, not the Docker context. internal/i18n and internal/templates are
# copied wholesale into the scratch image, so without this their *_test.go files
# would leak into production.
**/*_test.go
**/testdata/
.mutation/

